properties.Name: StorageTankPipeConstructionType
properties.Description:
The type of storage tank pipe construction.

Ex:
- Steel DW ( Bare Steel Double wall piping)
- Steel SW  ( Bare Steel Single wall piping)
- FG/FLEXDW  flexible piping made of a variety of materials)
- FG/FLEXSW (similar to the above, but with only a single wall)
